West Street, Bank Street, to Bethune Street. (Befora Reoonstruction).
President Sorough of Wanhatten.
724739f-a.folder: West Street & Bank Street, Manhattan, NY

724738f-a.text:
West Street, south from Bank Street, opposite Pier 49, North River, showing the West Side Elevated Highway under construction. This is the first link to be built, and runs from 23rd Street to just north of Canal Street. See the view at Spring Street, October
27 of this year.
Summer 1930.
Ewing Galloway.
Ne. ~2627
